    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Thanks for your feedback, however this is an engine limitation. You have two options here: \r\n\r\n1. statically say which items the menu has\r\n2. make the answer return the facet, even if it has 0 results\r\n\r\nThe second option would be the preferable for you, but it's not possible. I did put it on our internal feedback board. \r\n\r\nduplicate of https://github.com/algolia/algoliasearch-client-javascript/issues/541",
